2825 this act or any other appropriation or appropriations or
2826 portion thereof hereby made not in and of itself
2827 unconstitutional or invalid.
2828 Section 22. All laws or parts of laws, general,
2829 special, private, or local in conflict with or inconsistent
2830 with the provisions of this act are hereby expressly repealed.
2831 Section 23. This act shall become effective on October
2832 1, 2026.
